---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';

// 在组件脚本中可以定义变量、导入数据或执行JavaScript
const pageTitle = "Astro 组件演示";

// 示例数据
const cards = [
  {
    title: "Astro 组件",
    body: "Astro 组件是构建 Astro 网站的基本单元，它们是纯静态的HTML片段。",
    href: "https://docs.astro.build/zh-cn/core-concepts/astro-components/"
  },
  {
    title: "Astro 布局",
    body: "布局组件帮助你共享常见的UI结构，如页眉、导航栏和页脚。",
    href: "https://docs.astro.build/zh-cn/core-concepts/layouts/"
  },
  {
    title: "Astro 路由",
    body: "Astro 使用基于文件的路由系统，src/pages/ 目录中的每个 .astro 文件都成为一个页面。",
    href: "https://docs.astro.build/zh-cn/core-concepts/routing/"
  }
];
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
    
    <p class="intro">
      这个页面展示了如何在 Astro 中创建和使用组件。下面的卡片是使用同一个 <code>Card.astro</code> 组件渲染的，
      但每个卡片接收不同的属性（props）。
    </p>
    
    <section class="cards">
      {cards.map(card => (
        <Card
          title={card.title}
          body={card.body}
          href={card.href}
        />
      ))}
    </section>
    
    <div class="code-example">
      <h2>组件用法示例</h2>
      <pre><code>---
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

&lt;Card
  title="卡片标题"
  body="卡片内容描述"
  href="https://example.com"
/&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="navigation">
      <a href="/" class="button">返回首页</a>
      <a href="/guide" class="button secondary">查看指南</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #4f39fa;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #4b5563;
  }
  
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .code-example {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .code-example h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  pre {
    background-color: #f3f4f6;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  
  code {
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  
  .navigation {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .button.secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #3245ff;
    border: 1px solid #3245ff;
  }
  
  .button:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>